org.matsim.contrib.noise

Class NoiseConfigGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.core.config.ConfigGroup
      • org.matsim.core.config.ReflectiveConfigGroup
        • org.matsim.contrib.noise.NoiseConfigGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MatsimExtensionPoint

    public final class NoiseConfigGroup
extends ReflectiveConfigGroup
    Provides the parameters required to build a simple grid with some basic spatial functionality. Provides the parameters required to compute noise emissions, immissions and damages.
    Author:
    ikaddoura
